snippet.textDisplay: There is to many scams like this that has been going on a long time now. I sell of websites as well and the most recent scam is people contact you asking to buy but they say, you must put in a six digit code to see if the seller is legitimate. That is a lie, the code is to hack your phone or computer in real time so they can steal from your bank account and do identity theft. Be aware of that scam as well please.
